fields.name: USGIN Minimum Metadata Set
fields.purpose: Provides bare-minimum validation for USGIN-profile metadata records

fields.name: Abstract exists for Dataset
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset must have an abstract

fields.name: CI_Citation DateTime for Dataset is Valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset CI_Citations DateTime must be an ISO 8601 formatted string

fields.name: CI_Citation DateTypeCode codeList for Dataset is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset CI_Citations DateTypeCode codeList must be defined

fields.name: CI_Citation DateTypeCode codeListValue for Dataset is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset CI_Citations DateTypeCode codeListValue must be defined

fields.name: CI_Citation RoleCode codeList for Dataset is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset CI_Citations RoleCode codeList is valid

fields.name: CI_Citation RoleCode codeListValue for Dataset is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset CI_Citations RoleCode codeListValue is valid

fields.name: CI_Citation in Dataset Identification
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Datasets require CI_Citation

fields.name: CI_Citation in Dataset Requires a Title
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset CI_Citations require a title

fields.name: CharacterSetCode codeList is Valid
fields.description: Checks that the CharacterSetCode attrribute codeList is correct

fields.name: CharacterSetCode codeListValue is Valid
fields.description: Checks that the CharacterSetCode attrribute codeListValue is correct

fields.name: Dataset CI_Citation DateTime Looks Like ISO
fields.description: Dataset CI_Citations DateTime must be an ISO 8601 formatted string

fields.name: Dataset CI_Citation DateTypeCode codeList is valid
fields.description: Dataset CI_Citations DateTypeCode codeList is correct

fields.name: Dataset CI_Citation DateTypeCode codeListValue is valid
fields.description: Dataset CI_Citations DateTypeCode codeListValue is correct

fields.name: Dataset CI_Citation Requires a Title
fields.description: Checks that Dataset CI_Citations have a title

fields.name: Dataset CI_Citation RoleCode codeLisValue is valid
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that CI_Citations RoleCode codeListValue is valid

fields.name: Dataset CI_Citation RoleCode codeList is valid
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that CI_Citations RoleCode codeList is valid

fields.name: Dataset Intellectual Contact must have a named entity
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that Resource contact has at least one of: individualName, organisationName, postionName

fields.name: Dataset Intellectual Contact must have a some Contact Info
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that Resource contact has at least one of: phone, deliveryPoint, email

fields.name: Dataset Resource Language Code is Valid
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that Resource Language Code is a valid ISO639-2 three-letter code

fields.name: Dataset Status codeList is valid
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that Status codeList is valid

fields.name: Dataset Status codeListValue is valid
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that Status codeListValue is valid

fields.name: Dataset has an Abstract
fields.description: For a Dataset: Checks that an abstract is present

fields.name: Datasets must contain a CI_Citation
fields.description: Checks that dataset records contain a CI_Citation

fields.name: DateStamp looks like an ISO date
fields.description: Checks that the DateStamp looks like an ISO-style datetime

fields.name: Distribution Format is Included
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: When distribution information is present, a distribution format is required

fields.name: Distribution Information is Included
fields.description: For use in conditional rules: Checks MD_Distribution is present

fields.name: Distribution Information requires Distribution Format
fields.description: Checks that when distribution information is present, a distribution format is present

fields.name: Distribution Information requires Distributor with Named Entity
fields.description: Checks that when distribution information is present, a distributor is present with a named entity

fields.name: Distribution Information requires Transfer Options
fields.description: Checks that when distribution information is present, transfer options are present

fields.name: Distribution Information requires that Distributor RoleCode codeList is Valid
fields.description: Where Distribution info is present: Checks that distributor RoleCode codeList is valid

fields.name: Distribution Information requires that Distributor RoleCode codeListValue is valid
fields.description: Where Distribution info is present: Checks that distributor RoleCode codeListValue is valid

fields.name: Distributor RoleCode codeList is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Distributor RoleCode codeList is valid

fields.name: Distributor RoleCode codeListValue is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Distributor RoleCode codeListValue is valid

fields.name: Distributor has a named Entity
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: When distribution information is present, a distributor is required with a named entity

fields.name: Has File Identifier
fields.description: Checks that metadata hase a file identifier

fields.name: HierarchyLevel codeList is Valid
fields.description: Checks that the HierarchyLevel attrribute codeList is correct

fields.name: HierarchyLevel codeListValue is Valid
fields.description: Checks that the HierarchyLevel attrribute codeListValue is correct

fields.name: HierarchyLevelName is Valid
fields.description: Checks that the HierarchyLevelName value is valid

fields.name: Icon is labeled
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Checks that an icon is present

fields.name: If Metadata Contact provides an Icon, a URL must be provided
fields.description: Checks that where an Icon is listed, something looking like a URL is also provided

fields.name: Intellectual Contact for Dataset must have a named entity
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Checks that Intellectual contact has at least one of: individualName, organisationName, postionName

fields.name: Intellectual Contact for Dataset must have a some Contact Info
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Checks that Intellectual contact has at least one of: phone, deliveryPoint, email

fields.name: Language Code is Valid
fields.description: Checks that Language Code is a valid ISO639-2 three-letter code

fields.name: Metadata Contact Role codeList is Valid
fields.description: Checks that the Metadata Contact Role has a valid codeList value

fields.name: Metadata Contact Role codeListValue is Valid
fields.description: Checks that the Metadata Contact Role has a valid codeListValue value

fields.name: Metadata Contact must have a named entity
fields.description: Checks that Metadata contact has at least one of: individualName, organisationName, positionName

fields.name: Metadata Contact must have an email address
fields.description: Checks that Metadata Contact contains something that looks like an email address

fields.name: Metadata Standard Name is identified
fields.description: Checks that the Metadata Standard Name identifies this record as ISO-NAP-USGIN

fields.name: Metadata Standard Version is identified
fields.description: Checks that the Metadata Standard Version is identified

fields.name: Record is a Dataset
fields.description: Checks that MD_DataIdentification is present

fields.name: Resource Identification is Required
fields.description: At least one of MD_DataIdentification (dataset, dataset series) or SV_ServiceIdentification (service) is required

fields.name: Resource Language Code for Dataset is Valid
fields.description: For use in conditional: Checks that Dataset Resource Language Code is a valid ISO639-2 three-letter code

fields.name: Status codeList for Dataset is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset Status codeList is valid

fields.name: Status codeListValue for Dataset is valid
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: Dataset Status codeListValue is valid

fields.name: Transfer Options are Included
fields.description: For use in conditional rule: When distribution information is present, a transfer options are required

fields.name: URL is required
fields.description: For user in conditional rule: When icon is present, a URL is required
